      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty\u2014it is absolutely flawless! I've babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is spotless. It's been garage-kept and meticulously cared for. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
