    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered via the S65 4.0L V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, mated to a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. This specimen exhibits zero subframe stress and has undergone proactive rod bearing service with Blackstone oil analysis records. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping coefficients, and the M Variable Differential Lock operates with surgical precision. Cosmetically, the finish remains in factory-delivered state, free of rock chips or interior leather fatigue. A mechanically flawless, turn-key example for the purist.",
