    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps and no history of paintwork. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains soft and supple without a single crease, and the original factory scent is still present. All interior electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the navigation interface, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It comes with a complete, documented service history from an authorized dealership, showing preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with silk-like precision, and the undercarriage remains free of any road debris or corrosion. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a turn-key vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
